title: Gold Spanning Wings Watch Face
summary: Wings swing in to position as you tell the time.
description: The golden wings are a sign of honor. Wear it proud on this watch face. The wings about the gold skull swing up into position as you activate the screen on your watch face. Enjoy the wings every time you tell the time. You can choose from a variety of background colors which appear in a rugged fashion in the background. The time and date are shown in a powerful golden color. The time can be told in 12 and 24 hour modes. The date is told in numerical format. Download this gold skull watch face to feel like a special forces unit of your own. When downloading this watch face, be sure to download Android Wear for smartwatches. Android Wear will allow you to install this gold wings watch face on to your wear device.
